Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:40.04,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-I am the p-president of...}T-Tôi là h-hội trưởng...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:51.41,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,K-Kom—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:57.87,Default,Shikiya,0,0,0,,{Literature club.}CLB Văn học.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.50,Default,Shikiya,0,0,0,,Komari Chika.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.65,Default,Shikiya,0,0,0,,{Glad to make your acquaintance.}Mong được giúp đỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:12.23,Default,Tiara,0,0,0,,{All right, then. Please continue \Nwith your activity report.}Vậy thì tiếp theo đến phần báo cáo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:15.03,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-I, um, yes... Ah!}V-vâng ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.32,Default,Tiara,0,0,0,,{Literature club, are you good?}CLB Văn học ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:19.03,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:24.75,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Yes, I-I'm...}Vâng, t-tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:27.66,Default,Tiara,0,0,0,,{If you have nothing to report, \Nwe'll move on to the broadcast club.}Nếu không có gì báo cáo thì qua CLB phát thanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:30.26,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Huh? U-Um, p-please w-wai—}Hả? C-Chờ đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:32.42,Default,Tiara,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, but we're behind schedule.}Xin lỗi nhưng chúng ta bị trễ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:36.79,Default,Tiara,0,0,0,,{All right. Broadcast club, \Nyour report, please.}Tiếp theo, mời CLB phát thanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.84,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Unfortunately, Komari's \Nchallenge ended in defeat.}Đáng tiếc, thử thách cho hội\N trưởng CLB Komari đã thất bại.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:48.52,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Everyone else will probably forget \Nwhat happened here in a couple of days.}Mọi người sẽ quên việc này sau 2,3 ngày.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:52.17,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{But it won't be that easy for Komari.}Nhưng với Komari thì không.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:58.21,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{She'll probably carry a painful memory \Nof this day for a very long time.}Cậu ấy sẽ có một kí ức đau thương sau chuyện này.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:04.53,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I don't want to leave Komari \Nlooking like this in front of everyone.}Mình không muốn thấy Komari như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:12.08,Default,Broadcast Club President,0,0,0,,{This year, the broadcast club handled \Nschool announcements for Tsuwabuki Fest,}Năm nay CLB phát sóng đã lo phần \Nthông tin về lễ hội trường Tsuwabuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:15.46,Default,Broadcast Club President,0,0,0,,{as well as live commentary \Nfor sports day activities...}cũng như bình luận trực tiếp về các sự kiện...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:17.16,Default,Tiara,0,0,0,,{What do you want?}Cậu cần gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.51,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I apologize for being late.}Tôi xin lỗi vì đến trễ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.84,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I'm the president of the literature club,\N Nukumizu Kazuhiko.}Tôi là hội trưởng CLB Văn học, Nukumizu Kazuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.44,Default,Tiara,0,0,0,,{I don't see your name on the list.}Tôi không thấy tên cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:30.26,Default,Tiara,0,0,0,,{Did you complete the paperwork \Nto become president?}Đã hoàn thành đơn chuyển đổi vai trò chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:34.40,Default,Hokobaru,0,0,0,,{The paperwork is just a formality.\N Please continue.}Cứ để giấy tờ làm sau, tiếp tục đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:37.18,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{All right. Thank you very much.}Vâng, cảm ơn ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:40.47,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{N-Nukumizu. What are you doing here?}N-Nukumizu, cậu làm gì ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:42.65,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Just let me take over here.}Để tớ xử lý cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.32,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{S-Screw you!}Đ-Đừng có đùa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:52.66,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{D-Don't you understand \Nwhat this m-means to me?!}C-Cậu có hiểu cảm xúc của tôi không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.54,Default,Tiara,0,0,0,,{Uh, are you all right?}C-Cậu ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.11,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I'm fine.}Không sao ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:06.39,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Here is the literature club's activity report.}Đây là báo cáo hoạt động CLB văn học.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.44,Default,Club President 1,0,0,0,,{I'm so hungry.}Đói quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:11.01,Default,Club President 2,0,0,0,,{Wanna go get crêpes?}Muốn ăn crepe không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.72,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Now you've gone and done it.}Xong phim rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:17.24,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I know I did.}Tớ đã làm mất rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:20.31,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I understand what you were trying to do,}Tớ hiểu việc cậu định làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:25.98,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{but I'm sure Komari-chan \Nhates the idea that you're a jerk.}Nhưng Komari hẳn sẽ ghét cậu lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.95,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Here, I'll give you the \Nlast one, Nukumizu-kun!}Đây, tớ sẽ cho cậu cái cuối cùng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:39.59,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Why is there only one left?}Ăn gì hết cả hộp bánh vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.71,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Anyway, I've got to go after Komari.}Tóm lại phải đuổi theo Komari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.08,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I'll let everyone know.}Tớ sẽ thông báo mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.49,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Did you find Komari-chan?}Có thấy Komari-chan không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:03.75,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{She's small and has short, wavy hair...}Cậu ấy nhỏ người, tóc hơi bồng bềnh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:10.07,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Her bike's still here. \NShe must be on campus somewhere.}Xe đạp vẫn ở đây, chắc chắn phải trong trường.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:32.20,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why did you do it?}T-Tại sao cậu lại làm vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:35.56,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry. I know I was out of line.}Xin lỗi vì đã xen vào chuyện của cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:37.35,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{You were way out of line!}Đúng vậy đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:42.02,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{B-But why did you? \NI-I told you I could do it myself.}T-Tại sao chứ? T-Tôi đã bảo tự làm rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:47.36,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-I needed to show them I could! \NN-Nukumizu, why are you always...}T-Tôi phải cho họ thấy thành quả. \NT-Tại sao lúc nào cậu cũng...
